The article is a presidential memorandum issued by President Donald J. Trump on July 22, 2019. The memorandum states that the President has determined that the domestic production capability for separation and processing of Light Rare Earth Elements is essential to national defense. The President further states that without his action, the United States industry cannot be expected to provide this capability adequately and in a timely manner. The memorandum authorizes and directs the Secretary of Defense to publish this memorandum in the Federal Register.